blocks.saveContent: On 15th December 2021, FLS Group celebrated the company's brand relaunch by sending the CEO's business card to the edge of outer space. The epic delivery highlighted how FLS’s supply chain expertise covers the world with Tailor-Made Global Solutions.

blocks.saveContent: The FLS Group team crafts and delivers out-of-the-box solutions to the most challenging logistics across every supply chain. After almost three decades of success, FLS has expanded into a group of interconnected business divisions, including FLS Projects, FLS Logistics, FLS Warehousing and FLS Trading. From 13 offices in 9 countries around the world: Thailand, Vietnam, Myanmar, Australia, Singapore, Indonesia, USA, Taiwan and Malaysia, FLS Group serves customers in the automotive, chemicals, energy, food, industrial manufacturing, medical devices and offshore industries.
